Package org.apache.manifoldcf.crawler.common.filenet

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFilenet
    This class abstracts away from the filenet methods necessary to "do things" that the crawler or authority needs to be done with the Filenet repository.
    IFilenetFactory
    This interface describes a factory for producing remote IFilenet objects under the auspices of RMI.
